sentence: i'd like the lowest nonstop round trip coach class fares from miami to new york
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.round_trip_cost, '"'||v9.fare_basis_code||'"',
 '"'||v9.class_type||'"', '"'||v10.fare_id||'"', '"'||v11.flight_id||'"',
 v11.stops, '"'||v12.airport_code||'"', '"'||v13.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v13.city_name||'"', '"'||v14.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v15.city_code||'"', '"'||v15.city_name||'"' FROM fare v0,
 fare_basis v9, flight_fare v10, flight v11,
 airport_service v12, city v13, airport_service v14, city v15 
WHERE ((v0.round_trip_cost = (
SELECT MIN (v1.round_trip_cost) FROM fare v1 
WHERE ((v1.fare_basis_code IN (
SELECT v2.fare_basis_code FROM fare_basis v2 
WHERE (v2.class_type = 'COACH'))) 
AND (v1.fare_id IN (
SELECT v3.fare_id FROM flight_fare v3 
WHERE (v3.flight_id IN (
SELECT v4.flight_id FROM flight v4 
WHERE ((v4.stops =  0) AND ((v4.from_airport IN (
SELECT v5.airport_code FROM airport_service v5 
WHERE (v5.city_code IN (
SELECT v6.city_code FROM city v6 
WHERE (v6.city_name = 'MIAMI'))))) 
AND (v4.to_airport IN (
SELECT v7.airport_code FROM airport_service v7 
WHERE (v7.city_code IN (
SELECT v8.city_code FROM city v8 
WHERE (v8.city_name = 'NEW YORK')))))))))))))) 
AND (((v0.fare_basis_code = ANY v9.fare_basis_code) 
AND (v9.class_type = 'COACH')) AND ((v0.fare_id = ANY v10.fare_id) 
AND ((v10.flight_id = ANY v11.flight_id) AND ((v11.stops =  0) 
AND (((v11.from_airport = ANY v12.airport_code) 
AND ((v12.city_code = ANY v13.city_code) AND (v13.city_name = 'MIAMI'))) 
AND ((v11.to_airport = ANY v14.airport_code) AND ((v14.city_code = ANY v15.city_code) 
AND (v15.city_name = 'NEW YORK')))))))));
